Text:
This is my first torrent, and I'm really confused!

My upload speed maxes out at around 280 kB/s when I'm seeding torrents I download.  I'm using uTorrent 3.0.1, and have chosen "force start" and "initial seeding" but the speed is still less than 25 kB/s!  It's also the only torrent I have active...

Any thoughts?
I turned off "initial seeding" and my upload rate immediately shot up to 280 kB/s! WTF!?!?
